content: MAKI INUMAKI INU "aims to be a decentralized and financially free community"MAKI INU, which was launched in the BSC network in the last quarter of 2022,will actively start trading on the Pancakeswap stock market on January 01,2023 and will soon become one of the world's leading projects and take itsplace in all major stock markets, respectively.With the Play to Burn game, which we will launch in the 2nd quarter of 2023,we will both achieve price stability and reduce my current supply by sendingthe MAKI INU tokens earned by our users within the game once a month.
